## .rule = forbid-gerunds

### .what
gerunds (-ing as nouns) forbidden

### .scope
- code: variable names, function names, class names, comments
- docs: markdown, readmes, briefs, prompts
- logs: error messages, debug output
- comms: commit messages, pr descriptions, slack

### .why
gerunds vague, obscure noun/verb, meanings drift, hide agency, bloat, alternatives clearer

### .termsmell
gerunds signal unclear domain: lazy placeholder

### .see also
pairs with rule.require.order.noun_adj

### .enforcement
gerund usage = blocker

